title: Alaskan Mysteries - Sue Henry
description:
Sue Henry (born 1940) is an author of mystery thriller fiction. She has also been a college administrator and instructor at the University of Alaska and has lived in Anchorage, Alaska since the 1970s. She brings history, Alaskan lore, and the majestic beauty of the vast landscape to her mysteries.
